OL,3,CPhotos of jewellery released after
OL,4,Cwoman's body found in woods
OL,6,FA woman's body has been found in
OL,7,Fwoodland in Camborne, Cornwall.
OL,9,FPolice received reports of a body in
OL,10,Fthe Killivose area at 7:45am on Sunday
OL,11,F3 May.
OL,13,FOfficers have released images of her
OL,14,Fjewellery in the hope that somebody
OL,15,Fmight recognise it and help with the
OL,16,Fidentification of the body.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/2
