OL,3,CPhotos of jewellery released after
OL,4,Cwoman's body found in woods
OL,6,FAccording to Devon and Cornwall
OL,7,FPolice, detectives have been working
OL,8,Fto establish the woman's identity and
OL,9,Fthe exact circumstances surrounding
OL,10,Fher death, which is being treated as
OL,11,Funexplained.
OL,13,FThe force does not believe it to be
OL,14,Fsuspicious at this time.
